	<descriptionlist>
		<description><![CDATA[
			Ayeris, Unleashed!<br/> 
Winterboard is buggy, slow and really outdated, with Snowboard and Anemone now the main theme engines I decided to port the stunning theme to work with iOS 7 onwards.<br/> 
<br/> 
Enjoy!<br/>
<br/>
<b>Credits:</description></b><br/>
@Geek_Break and @Sn0wCooder for originally porting the theme, @DeloExtra for work with the Calendar icon and @PandoConnection for adding functionallity with Snowboard.
]]>
</description>
